OL,3,CUniversity leader suspended after
OL,4,C'serious allegations'
OL,6,FThe vice-chancellor of the University
OL,7,Fof Greater Manchester has been
OL,8,Fsuspended following "serious
OL,9,Fallegations".
OL,11,FProfessor George Holmes, who has led
OL,12,Fthe university for 20 years, has been
OL,13,Fsuspended alongside the Provost and a
OL,14,Fsenior member of academic staff at the
OL,15,Finstitution, formerly known as the
OL,16,FUniversity of Bolton.
OL,18,FIt comes after the university
OL,19,Fcommissioned an independent
OL,20,Finvestigation into recent allegations
OL,21,Fmade about the institution in Bolton.
