OL,3,CUniversity leader suspended after
OL,4,C'serious allegations'
OL,6,FLucy Powell, leader of the House of
OL,7,FCommons, told MPs in March that the
OL,8,Fpolice and the Office for Students
OL,9,F(OfS) were investigating "serious
OL,10,Fallegations" of racism, bullying and
OL,11,Ffinancial misconduct at the university.
OL,13,FHer comments came after Phil Brickell,
OL,14,Fthe Labour MP for Bolton West, said he
OL,15,Fhad been contacted by whistleblowers
OL,16,Fwith further allegations about
OL,17,F"concerning practices" at the
OL,18,Funiversity.
