OL,3,CUniversity leader suspended after
OL,4,C'serious allegations'
OL,6,FA statement by the university said it
OL,7,F"was made aware of PwC's findings
OL,8,Ffollowing its investigation into
OL,9,Fserious allegations raised in the
OL,10,Fmedia and subsequently in Parliament."
OL,12,FIt confirmed that the vice-chancellor,
OL,13,Fthe Provost and a senior member of
OL,14,Facademic staff had been suspended
OL,15,Fafter "serious allegations".
OL,17,FThe statement added: "These
OL,18,Fsuspensions are a precautionary
OL,19,Fmeasure and do not imply any
OL,20,Fassumption of guilt.
