OL,6,F"The university has taken this step to
OL,7,Fensure a fair and transparent process.
OL,9,F"As the university's internal
OL,10,Fprocedures, involving all relevant
OL,11,Fparties, have now begun, we are not
OL,12,Fable to comment further until such
OL,13,Fmatters are concluded."
OL,15,FDr Greg Walker, pro vice chancellor
OL,16,F(academic), has assumed the role of
OL,17,Facting vice-chancellor and interim
OL,18,Faccountable officer during the
OL,19,Finvestigation.
